=== GAP_MEMORIAL ===
# id: 65
# title: The Gap Memorial
# chinese_title: 断代纪念碑
# category: Lore
# mode: dungeon

A solemn monument stands in what was once the station's atrium. Holographic names scroll endlessly — those lost during the Gap, when all memory and records simply vanished. Someone has left fresh flowers at the base, impossibly, in this abandoned place.

* [Pay your respects and read the names]
  ~ gain_radical("人")
  "念" (niàn) — to remember, to miss. The radical "人" (rén) means person.
* [Investigate who left the flowers]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "花" (huā) — flower
* [Record the memorial for posterity]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "史" (shǐ) — history
* [Search the monument base for hidden compartments]
  ~ gain_gold(15)
  "底" (dǐ) — bottom, base
